To install from a clean pull using 'make' (GNU make):

mkdir out
cd out
cmake -DCMAKE_EXPORT_COMPILE_COMMANDS=1 -G "Unix Makefiles" ../Init.cmake ..
make

To install from a clean pull using 'ninja' (Ninja):
mkdir out
cd out
cmake -DCMAKE_EXPORT_COMPILE_COMMANDS=1 -G "Ninja" -C ../Init.cmake ..
ninja

To run Infer:
infer run --compilation-database compile_commands.json
